Here's season 1 of the fantastic Star Trek TNG for Blu-Ray
remasters, reencoded to a more suitable file size by kris33!

Like with Season 2, 3 and 4 (already uploaded to TPB and Kickass.to),
I've reencoded the high bitrate scene source with x264 using
the &quot;very slow&quot; preset, which resulted in a much smaller 
file size, yet with 85-90% of the quality still remaining.
Some grain in the source is not visible anymore, but that's about it.

Check out the Sample before you dismiss this upload blindly
due to being scared of the small file size. 

The audio has been converted from 5.1 DTS 1500 KBps to 
2.0 Dolby Pro Logic II AAC 192 KBps. The difference is
inaudible on non-surround speakers.

Enjoy and please keep seeding it! I also appreciate comments and 
upvotes on TPB and KickassTorrents :)




